Description: Beaver platform core (braille-first, terminal-only)
 Beaver is a braille-first, terminal-only platform built on Raspberry Pi OS Lite.
 .
 This package installs the minimal core toolset required for a usable, supportable
 console environment, including BRLTTY, essential documentation tools, and basic
 diagnostics utilities. Networking and optional features are provided by other
 Beaver meta-packages.
Homepage: https://github.com/stwelebny/beaver

